column2: "A white fortress, and a black fortress."
"Fufu, this is nice, being here with <%me>, side by side."
"It's all thanks to Xiao that I got a special approval to join ARKS. ...Hmm?"
"Huge... Are they natives of this planet?"
"Uu... Their language hasn't been translated yet... I can't make out a word..."
"That person... The aura he gives off is somehow different from the others."
"Ah, geez! I get the feeling that I'm being worshiped, but I don't get what they're saying at all!"
"<%me>! We'll get nowhere at this rate. Let's head back and consult Xiao."
